'''Adjudicator''' was a basic design of [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] [[Lightsaber hilt/Legends|hilt]] that was used by members of the [[New Jedi Order]] as of [[14 ABY/Legends|14 ABY]]. A [[Unidentified Jedi student|certain Jedi student]] used a weapon of this type of construction.

